{\fs20 \par \par \par }{\f8\fs20\b\i0 The Department of Rehabilitation }{\fs20 offers many services  free to help those with disabilities to get work and live independently,  including vocational counseling and training; job placement; medical treatment; support  for tuition and books; necessary tools; car modifications; money for transportation; reader and interpreter services: and services for family members (such as driving lessons or counseling).\par Call the }
